# UFree App - Cline AI Context & Rules

## Project Overview & Architecture
- **App:** UFree (iOS Mobile App).
- [cite_start]**Data Flow:** UI → ViewModel → CompositeRepository → SwiftData (instant) + Firestore (background)[cite: 712].
- [cite_start]**APNs**: Implement background notifications using the FCM bridge and Hybrid Listener strategy [cite: 659-664].

## Performance & Caching
- [cite_start]**Optimization Goal**: Maintain <5s cold starts by reusing established caches[cite: 302].
- **Mandatory Flags**: For any build/test, always include:
  - [cite_start]`derived_data_path: "./fastlane/builds/DerivedData"` 
  - [cite_start]`-skipPackagePluginValidation -clonedSourcePackagesDirPath ./fastlane/spm_cache` 

## Testing Protocol
- [cite_start]**Source of Truth**: Use `bundle exec fastlane tests` for all pre-flight checks.
- [cite_start]**Selective Execution**: For UI tweaks, run targeted tests for the specific component before running the full suite.
- [cite_start]**Efficiency**: Only run tests if logic changes; skip for documentation or comments.

## Terminal & API Limit Protections
- **The Token Explosion Rule**: Massive logs cause hangs. [cite_start]Never read full logs in the terminal[cite: 726, 731].
- **Silent Operator Protocol**: 
  1. [cite_start]Pipe all build/test output to `build.log`.
  2. [cite_start]Use `tail` or `grep` to verify success or triage specific errors.
  3. [cite_start]Do not print progress bars or verbose output[cite: 728].
- [cite_start]**The "Two Strike" Rule**: If a command fails twice, stop and wait for human guidance[cite: 731, 732].

## Git Commit Convention
- [cite_start]Pattern: `(TYPE) brief description in mostly lowercase`[cite: 723].
- [cite_start]Valid Types: (FEAT), (FIX), (CHORE), (REFACTOR), (TEST), (DOCS)[cite: 724].